flowchart TD
    A[POST /v1/chat] --> B[run_rag_agent_turn]
    B --> C{Route mode}
    C -->|rag| R[RAG-only answer]
    C -->|db or both| D[Load live DB context]

    D --> E{Live context valid?}
    E -->|No| U[Fallback uploaded SQLite path or no DB data]
    E -->|Yes| F[Read query_mode]

    F --> G{query_mode}
    G -->|generated| GP[Generated DB pipeline]
    G -->|template_preferred| TP[Load+filter templates then try pick]
    G -->|template_only| TO[Load+filter templates then must pick]

    TO --> H{Any active templates?}
    H -->|No| ERR1[db_answer = No active templates error]
    H -->|Yes| I[Pick template index]

    TP --> I
    I --> J{Template picked?}
    J -->|No + template_only| ERR2[db_answer = No template matched error]
    J -->|No + template_preferred| GP
    J -->|Yes| K{Dialect}

    K -->|mysql/sql| L[Execute SQL template]
    K -->|mongodb| M[Execute Mongo template]

    L --> N{Execution OK?}
    M --> N
    N -->|No| ERR3[db_answer = SQL/Mongo error]
    N -->|Yes| OK[db_answer = query result JSON]

    GP --> Z[db_answer from generated pipeline]
    ERR1 --> Q
    ERR2 --> Q
    ERR3 --> Q
    OK --> Q
    Z --> Q
    R --> Q
    U --> Q

    Q[Final prompt includes db_answer] --> S[LLM writes natural-language reply]
